                  </origin>
                  <provenance>The chain-mark suggests that the book was at the College before <hi rend="italic">c.</hi> 1500. At the head of f. 1 is ‘Holcott super librum Sapientiae’, s. xvii. ‘2’ is inked on the foredge. Inside the front board is the College bookplate and ‘B. 3. 8’ in modern pencil.</provenance>
